        "pages": "913--923",
        "publisher": "IEEE",
        "series": "{{TVCG}} '21",
        "shorttitle": "Chemicals in the {{Creek}}",
        "title": "Chemicals in the {{Creek}}: Designing a Situated Data Physicalization of Open Government Data with the Community",
        "type": "article",
        "url": "https://doi.org/10.1109/TVCG.2020.3030472",
